	<!-- ================================ Mechanoid Marshal ====================== -->
	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseMechanoidWalker">
		<defName>RM_Mech_Marshal</defName>
		<label>marshal</label>
		<statBases>
			<MoveSpeed>3.7</MoveSpeed>
			<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.25</ArmorRating_Blunt>
			<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.45</ArmorRating_Sharp>
		</statBases>
		<description>Fast human-sized, Sangheili-class, human-sized combat mechanoids specializing in rapid approach and close-range combat, whilst being able to withstand heavy fire. Their bodies are covered in points and blades, but they mostly use two arm blades to lop off limbs or gut their victims alive. Alternatively, they will use their head-mounted blade to ram enemies, also gutting them alive.</description>
		<tools>
			<li>
