	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseMechanoid">
		<defName>RM_Mech_Behemoth</defName>
		<label>behemoth</label>
		<description>Heavy, Mgalekgolo-class combat mechanoids that move slowly on two massive legs. Their thick carapace makes them very effective at drawing enemies fire. While heavily armored, their sensors require them to move in close to fire their weapons.</description>
